br.com.caelum.vraptor.http.route

Class DefaultRouteBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.caelum.vraptor.http.route.DefaultRouteBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RouteBuilder

    @Vetoed
public class DefaultRouteBuilder
extends Object
implements RouteBuilder
    Should be used in one of two ways, either configure the type and invoke the method or pass the method (java reflection) object. If not specified, the built route will have the lowest priority (higher value of priority), so will be the last to be used.
    Author:
    Guilherme Silveira
